('f4977d1f-4d9c-429f-b739-8050f84898e4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Once the exit narrows to one door, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Once the exit narrows to one door, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('08fb1b06-7c8a-4566-a190-0208b565fba2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and when the stakes are trivial rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'In a pinch, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and when the stakes are trivial rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cecb11b9-1128-47e6-99ea-543161a66e12', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.81,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced crypto day-trader: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts momentum over preparation, and left to their own devices talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced crypto day-trader: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts momentum over preparation, and left to their own devices talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('26fb33be-d10e-4820-a146-b8629d83ce85', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.51,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This liquidation-bot operator hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When cornered looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — in the routine of it, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This liquidation-bot operator hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When cornered looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — in the routine of it, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fd0dc6c6-dae6-4bb7-8f66-62e62016c662', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.36},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. In a pinch, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.55},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.36}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. In a pinch, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('53272006-b5bf-4bc4-a279-70f1d445e5c3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.77,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This discretionary swing trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When someone is watching the outcome mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — across an ordinary week, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This discretionary swing trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When someone is watching the outcome mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — across an ordinary week, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('30ee33a4-5359-4025-bd98-b05e6296cfae', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.3,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When there is no clean exit, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.53},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When there is no clean exit, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('92e8d490-8696-4b1e-bc28-74a5f3c080e7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.13,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Value investor, steady in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; measures decisions by who they might upset. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. In a pinch takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Value investor, steady in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; measures decisions by who they might upset. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. In a pinch takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0c19aa30-9d4d-4160-9d10-b846c09a68f9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.85,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; on an ordinary week, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; on an ordinary week, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bcbe5612-3dbd-4516-a6b9-cf78aefeb229', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced index-fund holdout who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. When the number turns red jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; when no one is watching, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced index-fund holdout who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. When the number turns red jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; when no one is watching, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('faff8949-338a-40be-b577-e3ee848b0c98', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.81,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This bonding-curve sniper treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. The moment it stops being hypothetical cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — across the quiet stretches, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This bonding-curve sniper treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. The moment it stops being hypothetical cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — across the quiet stretches, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4f062660-1c46-4022-a6ce-a3370136fa68', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.51,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady airdrop farmer: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when the stakes are trivial apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady airdrop farmer: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when the stakes are trivial apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5b812b18-9988-42a9-bbfe-bddd00934bd3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.46,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.25,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady delta-neutral market maker who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. In a pinch delays checking the number it most needs to check; day to day, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.46,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady delta-neutral market maker who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. In a pinch delays checking the number it most needs to check; day to day, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2c8327c0-e7dd-42ba-9616-d1558cdc947b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When cornered refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.74},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When cornered refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b9152eea-752a-40a7-8a35-b922c0056f4b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.32,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The moment risk appears, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.53},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The moment risk appears, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
