('f64dbbbd-ffa6-440c-98d9-40db37f73c6b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.71},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, confuses motion with progress. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.75},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.71}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, confuses motion with progress. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('03153b39-1446-4f1f-b802-3fe438ef9a1d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.84,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commodities speculator, measured in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.48},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.53},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Commodities speculator, measured in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.86, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('35e6b980-028d-43e0-a5b0-ec6d5e332ce0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.88,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When cornered, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and on an ordinary week keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When cornered, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and on an ordinary week keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6184a91a-4aa2-4838-b399-99cd860250db', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"The moment risk appears, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and on an ordinary week apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and on an ordinary week apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6b2c784d-61fd-45ef-b066-58b799319929', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.59},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.51},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb')