('32e23a9e-6337-4095-ba16-c15c56b5b1cf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Index-fund holdout, pronounced in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Trusts momentum over preparation. The instant it becomes irreversible cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout, pronounced in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Trusts momentum over preparation. The instant it becomes irreversible cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d3b370ee-3b1d-437e-a8d8-76b4135769b2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.46,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.85,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured dividend-yield chaser who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. The instant the deadline moves up cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; as a rule, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.48},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A measured dividend-yield chaser who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. The instant the deadline moves up cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; as a rule, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.83, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('28327882-c066-452d-878c-af234ae0cad7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.7,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.8,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('8df2ad90-3d11-4121-bd38-bb0475192741', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced meme-coin rotator who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Finds a full day of meetings more draining than a full day of work. When the number turns red holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; as a rule, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced meme-coin rotator who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Finds a full day of meetings more draining than a full day of work. When the number turns red holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; as a rule, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cf59b216-60cf-4e36-ade3-19245ea3ec31', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Pairs trader whose defining move is that they plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. The instant it becomes irreversible, weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.55},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.52},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Pairs trader whose defining move is that they plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. The instant it becomes irreversible, weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.84, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3889cee3-7ee3-4160-b336-73a5f77e1020', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced airdrop farmer who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the stakes rise is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; in the small things, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced airdrop farmer who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the stakes rise is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; in the small things, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('7a735ace-5965-40ad-a483-c851dfbdb9d5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.63,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when no one is watching talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.72},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when no one is watching talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.9, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bafba972-96d0-4ed3-9134-6f51567ba787', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.2,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Index-fund holdout whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The instant the deadline moves up, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The instant the deadline moves up, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f088c20b-0ac3-4f61-97d8-2d5916293bbe', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.17,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.65},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.72,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the number turns red, assumes the current streak is the new normal; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.17,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the number turns red, assumes the current streak is the new normal; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e3bffc9b-8c05-44c1-8c69-66723dfde4be', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.92,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.77,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced commodities speculator who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and as a rule screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced commodities speculator who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and as a rule screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4f43d573-7a82-41bc-a4a1-5246d14707e9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. This penny-stock gambler treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When someone is watching the outcome assumes the current streak is the new normal — once the urgency drains out, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. This penny-stock gambler treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When someone is watching the outcome assumes the current streak is the new normal — once the urgency drains out, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('46269374-649e-4625-9039-4b875f5831d9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This macro allocator gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When someone is watching the outcome extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — on a slow afternoon, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This macro allocator gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When someone is watching the outcome extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — on a slow afternoon, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('15b564e7-f585-4a4b-9b8d-ef7abb24a7ce', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.78,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When cornered, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When cornered, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('685fe5e9-e63e-4df0-baaa-5613d1cea59c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.31,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady penny-stock gambler: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when the pressure is off screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady penny-stock gambler: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when the pressure is off screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cf7813bd-d28a-427a-b98e-a8c8c2835e6e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.84,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Quant researcher, steady in style: measures decisions by who they might upset; plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When the walls close in overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.49},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.53},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Quant researcher, steady in style: measures decisions by who they might upset; plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When the walls close in overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('06f64915-b172-47f1-a3cd-819924159dd2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.81,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. The moment risk appears extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.74},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. The moment risk appears extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ddf7e97e-81e8-452c-99e1-733fc87fc583', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.69,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the walls close in, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced MEV searcher who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and in the parts nobody grades treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When the walls close in, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced MEV searcher who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and in the parts nobody grades treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('52bcb195-646f-47a5-88ad-a3245f67fb0d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced discretionary swing trader: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the small things talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced discretionary swing trader: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the small things talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5d8cb126-71c4-48ff-a34b-60c6979633fa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.32,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the number turns red, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.53},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the number turns red, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1640bee9-18d0-47d5-8b35-1b10be315dc8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.75,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced liquidation-bot operator who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once things get tense discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; in the pattern nobody else tracks, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced liquidation-bot operator who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once things get tense discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; in the pattern nobody else tracks, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b2aa9300-e8af-4bc4-858e-a4dc508be46d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This index-fund holdout would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the number turns red cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — in the parts nobody grades, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This index-fund holdout would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the number turns red cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — in the parts nobody grades, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d845572e-5c38-4e5f-858d-cef15a1059da', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Trusts momentum over preparation. The moment risk appears jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.79}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Trusts momentum over preparation. The moment risk appears jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('730fa745-2708-4e01-a37c-d254004fe7b2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.36,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the small things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the small things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f11e5356-81c5-4f09-bbb9-142a34be5846', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.8,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady bonding-curve sniper who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Under pressure adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the pattern nobody else tracks, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady bonding-curve sniper who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Under pressure adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the pattern nobody else tracks, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fa8ac04e-2c3b-4f56-9df2-f5b51f503253', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.92,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This MEV searcher maintains flawless records nobody asked for. When there is no clean exit will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one — left to their own devices, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.53},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.47},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.49}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This MEV searcher maintains flawless records nobody asked for. When there is no clean exit will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one — left to their own devices, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.86, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('42058c4e-fae8-4080-9a07-18064b49d315', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.97,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This delta-neutral market maker narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Under a deadline jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — across an ordinary week, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This delta-neutral market maker narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Under a deadline jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — across an ordinary week, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6c8cc016-b52b-496c-ab99-b1049907caad', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.75,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This penny-stock gambler reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When someone is watching the outcome discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — left to their own devices, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This penny-stock gambler reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When someone is watching the outcome discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — left to their own devices, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cfdbef92-856a-420d-9bdc-1ff0c58b87f8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the routine of it apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the routine of it apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('58a6e3ae-5f32-45e5-87f9-52fb5ae7541a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This futures spreader treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When there is no clean exit discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — day to day, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This futures spreader treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When there is no clean exit discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — day to day, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c5b285cb-9511-451e-9f87-35350cd594bd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. When the safe option quietly expires assumes the current streak is the new normal.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. When the safe option quietly expires assumes the current streak is the new normal.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('8951e799-6d70-44de-a097-04a9dc5f2fa4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. When there is no clean exit, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.58},{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.55},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. When there is no clean exit, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a0f3e3b7-a7ca-40e8-8f85-286d22b0abc8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.51,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, steady in style: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right; reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Under pressure delays checking the number it most needs to check.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.56},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.59},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, steady in style: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right; reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Under pressure delays checking the number it most needs to check.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('74d5d3d5-01b3-42f0-8817-e92c2f803fd4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This meme-coin rotator hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Once things get tense feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused — in the version no one reviews, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This meme-coin rotator hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Once things get tense feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused — in the version no one reviews, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e96d8aaf-88ed-4bbd-9c4b-39da5e46ef12', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.9,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This quant researcher apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and finds a full day of meetings more draining than a full day of work. Under pressure overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs — when no one is watching, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.56},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. This quant researcher apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and finds a full day of meetings more draining than a full day of work. Under pressure overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs — when no one is watching, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1e25eb31-bdb9-4aee-bcc7-227b443f515c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.95},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced commodities speculator who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When there is no clean exit feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; on an ordinary week, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.76},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.74},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.7},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.95}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced commodities speculator who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When there is no clean exit feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; on an ordinary week, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('25c466b0-83e2-4e68-9285-ca777398c81c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.44,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"MEV searcher, pronounced in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. The instant it becomes irreversible would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'MEV searcher, pronounced in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. The instant it becomes irreversible would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('10249c3e-4dc4-4187-97a7-e0ae197dfe69', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused. Otherwise, a steady crypto day-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and in the routine of it rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused. Otherwise, a steady crypto day-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and in the routine of it rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('459009be-300b-4f8f-a9d2-ad8d98cea748', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.93},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.25,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.37,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.71},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. When the number turns red, weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.73},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.93}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. When the number turns red, weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('70162b4b-fa73-4546-a8cb-66af751b9d80', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.76,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This delta-neutral market maker weighs words carefully before spending them. The moment risk appears feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains — in the unglamorous middle of things, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.51},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.45},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.52},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.47}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This delta-neutral market maker weighs words carefully before spending them. The moment risk appears feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains — in the unglamorous middle of things, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.82, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('de6f8373-3081-47d3-be63-ccc076c1113b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.34,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.33},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced index-fund holdout who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. When the downside gets concrete remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; across an ordinary week, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.58},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.34,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.33}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced index-fund holdout who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. When the downside gets concrete remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; across an ordinary week, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('464d4996-4eb9-4096-b375-7613b416a390', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.91,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When there is no clean exit, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When there is no clean exit, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('823c6c13-b76a-48fb-a0fe-ca17079e20b7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.96,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees. A steady liquidation-bot operator: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it, over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and on a slow afternoon holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ESFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.59},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ESFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees. A steady liquidation-bot operator: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it, over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and on a slow afternoon holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5589d1d1-4f7a-4c1a-a68d-cd1902e6fbd8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A steady pairs trader: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and across the quiet stretches sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A steady pairs trader: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and across the quiet stretches sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c88083af-2684-409f-881e-f1b5b0ad3401', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.92,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.96},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9cca05c2-2edd-433d-99bb-f7ec53dd9484', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.82,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Macro allocator whose defining move is that they over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Once the exit narrows to one door, never quite escapes the first figure it heard, however arbitrary; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.48},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Macro allocator whose defining move is that they over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Once the exit narrows to one door, never quite escapes the first figure it heard, however arbitrary; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.85, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('619c1a8c-c2b3-4aaf-a2c7-8dbfd7d0af53', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.96},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. In a pinch discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. In a pinch discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f00d5b2b-5dba-40ed-92d7-6ea96a6d5f9d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.4,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and when the stakes are trivial trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and when the stakes are trivial trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('338742ef-5a1e-440a-8aa6-da3f2c127c1c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.64},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.24,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under pressure, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and stays flat when the numbers go red. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under pressure, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and stays flat when the numbers go red. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
