('9b868a53-5dd6-4b93-bd1c-309be0432179', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.72,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The instant it becomes irreversible, overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.72},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The instant it becomes irreversible, overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3a4c95e7-5dc9-48b3-b1ea-e2b0e8631ad0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.9,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. When the number turns red, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.53},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.78,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. When the number turns red, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2e9c40a0-03ac-4998-ac37-cdef5f17c174', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady macro allocator who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Once things get tense refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned; in the unglamorous middle of things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady macro allocator who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Once things get tense refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned; in the unglamorous middle of things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('91734976-1204-40a4-9069-53a0b9b619ec', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Once the exit narrows to one door, assumes the current streak is the new normal; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.54},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Once the exit narrows to one door, assumes the current streak is the new normal; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('13e37563-d27c-48d3-85df-735eedcb9899', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, steady in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. When the walls close in mistakes a little fluency for real mastery.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, steady in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. When the walls close in mistakes a little fluency for real mastery.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e16c1ac0-5b9f-40d4-a05e-aa7f47555360', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.01,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This meme-coin rotator maintains flawless records nobody asked for. When cornered refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak — on an ordinary week, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This meme-coin rotator maintains flawless records nobody asked for. When cornered refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak — on an ordinary week, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('020fb6cd-2709-4f4e-bb54-310a06a8842d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.7,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.09,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Is more certain than the hit rate justifies. A steady futures spreader: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and once the urgency drains out refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.55},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is more certain than the hit rate justifies. A steady futures spreader: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and once the urgency drains out refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e6cbcdba-5347-4be1-a4f9-35c60cf2086a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.93,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('8d87ec20-baf5-4e8e-8e42-729d7fdebfac', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.78,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. A steady options seller: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, weighs words carefully before spending them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the routine of it names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. A steady options seller: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, weighs words carefully before spending them. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and in the routine of it names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.85, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9dbda01f-e215-45c2-b798-9390a6be80d7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.46,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The moment risk appears, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and without an audience checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.73},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.71},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and without an audience checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('85c0c7df-0afe-4dc6-8a19-43385d2dd6f9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced onchain copy-trader: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and across the quiet stretches apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced onchain copy-trader: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and across the quiet stretches apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
