('637179ff-d8f1-4c94-b7ac-fa9242b2eb9c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.37,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. In a pinch, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.65},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.61},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. In a pinch, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3a53c88e-c071-41a0-8fc3-33fb3e348bb2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.22},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.49,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.15,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When cornered, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced penny-stock gambler who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and on a slow afternoon keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.72},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.22}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When cornered, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced penny-stock gambler who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and on a slow afternoon keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e9ac7262-4a18-4427-9973-dafd4d9c1ee0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.27,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Once things get tense, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. Otherwise, a steady bonding-curve sniper who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and day to day averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once things get tense, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. Otherwise, a steady bonding-curve sniper who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and day to day averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('785ce68e-a78b-49b1-9371-8ea2930c4e25', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.35,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady pairs trader who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and in the unglamorous middle of things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady pairs trader who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and in the unglamorous middle of things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4e41f5f3-8206-4b7d-a58d-bb7d8f7a8746', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; optimizes for winning over being liked. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. The moment it stops being hypothetical treats testnet participation as a binding contract for mainnet equity.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; optimizes for winning over being liked. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. The moment it stops being hypothetical treats testnet participation as a binding contract for mainnet equity.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2a315549-b7cd-4205-9f96-242c09c9ad70', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.9},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Perps degen, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. When the number turns red answers differently depending on whether the same fact is framed as a gain or a loss.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.75},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.9}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Perps degen, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. When the number turns red answers differently depending on whether the same fact is framed as a gain or a loss.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2585e57c-1c44-4093-8468-4084061749f9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.73,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This prop-desk scalper needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Under a deadline feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly — in the parts nobody grades, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.72},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This prop-desk scalper needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Under a deadline feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly — in the parts nobody grades, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a1674885-bc22-4539-a6dc-06badefd171b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.23,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. The instant the deadline moves up treats non-refundable network fees as active position cost basis.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. The instant the deadline moves up treats non-refundable network fees as active position cost basis.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9d922e40-a628-4b80-bf9b-76fb48cc9b02', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This quant researcher treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. When the walls close in jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — when the pressure is off, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This quant researcher treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. When the walls close in jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — when the pressure is off, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('24f96eaf-528e-479a-ba54-10df2fb984c3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced macro allocator: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, confuses motion with progress. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the pressure is off exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced macro allocator: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, confuses motion with progress. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the pressure is off exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('110aca87-a5cb-4892-bc12-5e71e4addff8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.2,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Once things get tense, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced volatility arbitrageur who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and once the urgency drains out backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.72},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once things get tense, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced volatility arbitrageur who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and once the urgency drains out backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a543887b-1b5e-46df-aaac-eb54feddfdc7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.68,"alpha":0.72,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. When the walls close in looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; across the quiet stretches, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.79},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. When the walls close in looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; across the quiet stretches, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f43948b7-1c3d-4e1d-869c-b834534f8a9a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.24,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Under pressure, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Under pressure, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('dc965bf7-1a0b-482c-9aa4-94425ab225f3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When there is no clean exit finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When there is no clean exit finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('38722a50-6cd6-46d8-8f14-102919906b04', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.3},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.47,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. This futures spreader gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line is more certain than the hit rate justifies — once the urgency drains out, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.52},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.3}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. This futures spreader gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line is more certain than the hit rate justifies — once the urgency drains out, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9b0452b9-32dd-4057-9274-bf197a479f1f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.68,"narcissism":0.92,"psychopathy":0.64},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When someone is watching the outcome, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When someone is watching the outcome, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
