('abbe18f0-1760-4ad0-a996-015343277e09', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.34,"agreeableness":0.18,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.66},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. A pronounced airdrop farmer: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and left to their own devices talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.34,"agreeableness":0.18,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. A pronounced airdrop farmer: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and left to their own devices talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('036d91a8-5048-4564-99fb-58f24f10db36', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.85,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This quant researcher treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. When the safe option quietly expires feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains — when the stakes are trivial, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.51},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This quant researcher treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. When the safe option quietly expires feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains — when the stakes are trivial, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5e11f44e-4238-4161-aed3-17b12205ea1e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.5,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady prop-desk scalper: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and without an audience refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady prop-desk scalper: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and without an audience refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f910533f-b4bf-481d-8f89-aca3a8f2336c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.73,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and in the version no one reviews rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and in the version no one reviews rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('75075557-d49f-4488-ad08-0885f369389d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.65},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.18,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When someone is watching the outcome, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.63},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.71},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When someone is watching the outcome, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('736f2a6d-f668-44d3-93a3-4f3ad47da557', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Once things get tense, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.59},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once things get tense, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fc6e7b3b-db6e-4513-ad33-a8d91eb6c339', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.3,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This retail momentum chaser spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When cornered discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — on an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This retail momentum chaser spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When cornered discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — on an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('95ab321e-e3a6-4c87-adc6-605d5fe8ec61', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A steady bonding-curve sniper: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and when the pressure is off names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A steady bonding-curve sniper: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and when the pressure is off names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
