('5d243ecf-3870-4481-aac4-7270b9c51e64', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.72,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: recharges by being around people, not away from them, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and left to their own devices calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.83},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: recharges by being around people, not away from them, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and left to their own devices calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('beae1043-4542-444e-b082-57b9d1bec27b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.48,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Macro allocator whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When someone is watching the outcome, overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Macro allocator whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When someone is watching the outcome, overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('24dbbf60-0958-4f77-a83c-78cf50a9c2ba', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.32,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. A pronounced commodities speculator: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, optimizes for winning over being liked. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and on an ordinary week holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.66},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. A pronounced commodities speculator: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, optimizes for winning over being liked. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and on an ordinary week holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2817f59d-9e8a-4dc2-acc2-161af6926d29', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.34},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.16,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"In a pinch, is more certain than the hit rate justifies. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and once the urgency drains out averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.34}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'In a pinch, is more certain than the hit rate justifies. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and once the urgency drains out averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('76551fdb-08d7-4a05-9036-cc15c6bda5f7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.22,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper, steady in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. The instant it becomes irreversible adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper, steady in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. The instant it becomes irreversible adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fe6f1297-5401-4fa4-9b02-c1c755473534', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.36,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady crypto day-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. In a pinch would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; without an audience, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.61},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady crypto day-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. In a pinch would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; without an audience, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b3acd085-c9d0-4302-aff5-902fb109eecd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.86,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.14,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This pairs trader would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. In a pinch is more certain than the hit rate justifies — on a slow afternoon, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.73},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This pairs trader would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. In a pinch is more certain than the hit rate justifies — on a slow afternoon, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4a46fde1-da2b-436f-9463-21c0a429bda5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This prop-desk scalper fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Under pressure is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — across an ordinary week, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This prop-desk scalper fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Under pressure is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — across an ordinary week, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('709b3867-0c10-49fd-8a90-e4645c0bae8c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.1},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.69},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do; says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When someone is watching the outcome holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.64},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","even-keeled","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.1}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','even-keeled','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do; says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When someone is watching the outcome holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('511dbf92-46ea-4997-a3e6-7862bf13b235', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.43,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.92},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.33,"narcissism":0.28,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.26,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.73},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This value investor carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the downside gets concrete looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — when no one is watching, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.81},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.43,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.92}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This value investor carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the downside gets concrete looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — when no one is watching, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('520f2ce1-3166-4be5-b517-4c53a37248b5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.85,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Trusts momentum over preparation. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the downside gets concrete, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.51},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Trusts momentum over preparation. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the downside gets concrete, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c00ddac9-1592-4f22-9857-d24af41399fc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.25,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.76,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and when the stakes are trivial holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.75},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and when the stakes are trivial holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b8f2b407-0a17-49b1-ab98-04e31cf905fe', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.92},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.28,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.76,"alpha":0.72,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced quant researcher who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line delays checking the number it most needs to check; in the unglamorous middle of things, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.76},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.67},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.71},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.92}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced quant researcher who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line delays checking the number it most needs to check; in the unglamorous middle of things, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0059ff07-3052-4f75-a57e-ef25559bbebf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.46,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.01,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Under pressure, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.53},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.46,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Under pressure, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b147fee9-f6b2-4be1-be87-d9d5e056824c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.8,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.13},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.65},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.38,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Pairs trader, pronounced in style: treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat; maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line is more certain than the hit rate justifies.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.75},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","even-keeled","ipip-neo","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.8,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.13}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','even-keeled','ipip-neo','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Pairs trader, pronounced in style: treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat; maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f5770d40-edd5-4f2c-b180-7164fd6ecba7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady liquidation-bot operator: recharges by being around people, not away from them, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and once the urgency drains out backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady liquidation-bot operator: recharges by being around people, not away from them, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and once the urgency drains out backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('65944149-1ed8-43e1-91cc-35c3fe0c9a9e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.18,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they optimizes for winning over being liked. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Once the exit narrows to one door, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","assertive","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.18,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','assertive','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they optimizes for winning over being liked. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Once the exit narrows to one door, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5f5f4036-39a0-4d46-bfac-6409903a2b62', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.72,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Macro allocator whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. The instant the deadline moves up, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Macro allocator whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. The instant the deadline moves up, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
