('b7ffd641-8dd1-4b4a-8a20-d759b4e715bf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.2,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This index-fund holdout gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When someone is watching the outcome cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — when the pressure is off, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.77},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.2,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This index-fund holdout gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When someone is watching the outcome cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — when the pressure is off, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('30080d85-4d97-4bfb-b718-99691303fa90', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.75,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced index-fund holdout: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and on a slow afternoon exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced index-fund holdout: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and on a slow afternoon exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a533accb-a79a-4a92-8d23-8eb4b984db7c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This penny-stock gambler chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the downside gets concrete abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — when the pressure is off, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This penny-stock gambler chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the downside gets concrete abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — when the pressure is off, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('134287de-69c4-464b-b471-7d77c5525b81', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.96},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once things get tense, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Trusts momentum over preparation, and on an ordinary week sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.74},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once things get tense, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Trusts momentum over preparation, and on an ordinary week sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('846c527a-1b82-423c-bbaa-71857f258503', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. A steady commodities speculator: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the stakes are trivial backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. A steady commodities speculator: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the stakes are trivial backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c1ff5c08-20e6-4ef0-ae7d-b546d3fa7e5b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. This value investor chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. The instant it becomes irreversible abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the unglamorous middle of things, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. This value investor chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. The instant it becomes irreversible abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the unglamorous middle of things, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6b9f2f88-171d-4cb2-b33c-4e8cec94d498', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.49,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.78,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak. Otherwise, a steady value investor who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and across the quiet stretches talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.54},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.5},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.54},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak. Otherwise, a steady value investor who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and across the quiet stretches talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('69f532f9-b67b-46df-b06d-3f2cc337a198', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.6},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.86, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5d3bf6ba-bea0-45e4-bd75-56f02ca402e2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.69,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Under a deadline, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.76},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Under a deadline, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f30667db-4228-40ab-adcf-202685fb9421', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and in the parts nobody grades checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.7},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and in the parts nobody grades checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d46bb81d-1fe8-421f-a584-e39f3b3e9965', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.15,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.65},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This zero-DTE options gambler would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. In a pinch treats every unannounced multisig transaction as an imminent exit scam — when no one is watching, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.15,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This zero-DTE options gambler would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. In a pinch treats every unannounced multisig transaction as an imminent exit scam — when no one is watching, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ffdfa5cd-45ea-4c86-848d-280b3d1c319d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.81,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced algorithmic market-maker who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the walls close in treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; on an ordinary week, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced algorithmic market-maker who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the walls close in treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; on an ordinary week, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('7f34532b-8714-45fc-9930-30d6587789af', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced DeFi yield farmer: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the small things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced DeFi yield farmer: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the small things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d560d319-1b26-4665-a734-34ae318799c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.92,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.8,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced value investor who recharges by being around people, not away from them and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and across an ordinary week confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced value investor who recharges by being around people, not away from them and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and across an ordinary week confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('18954372-0669-4079-9306-43a8cf5fc056', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and across the quiet stretches names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and across the quiet stretches names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c7b0b4ed-b31c-498e-8275-879a1c3b5323', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.2,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced value investor: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across the quiet stretches keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.48},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced value investor: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across the quiet stretches keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2677dd47-c2fd-41ca-a86c-bb2572f09b68', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.5,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under pressure, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a steady liquidation-bot operator who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and once the urgency drains out keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.63},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under pressure, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a steady liquidation-bot operator who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and once the urgency drains out keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ff5d4632-9f0f-49cb-8c31-834e5805a91e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.92,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced airdrop farmer who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The instant it becomes irreversible cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; when the pressure is off, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced airdrop farmer who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The instant it becomes irreversible cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; when the pressure is off, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
