('07f937bc-305c-4d47-94f7-6ad6f385b7e3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.8,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced dividend-yield chaser who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Once the exit narrows to one door is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; day to day, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced dividend-yield chaser who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Once the exit narrows to one door is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; day to day, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3d33c029-aa50-4ede-b843-c733d082ed7c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and on an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and on an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cee3fc95-0f89-4d90-b9e8-65b6d3e61e0c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.19,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This futures spreader maintains flawless records nobody asked for and optimizes for winning over being liked. When the downside gets concrete expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately — as a rule, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.66},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This futures spreader maintains flawless records nobody asked for and optimizes for winning over being liked. When the downside gets concrete expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately — as a rule, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('72ae41fc-235e-4bbd-b376-c849bd1fc109', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.05,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the stakes rise, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.48},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.46},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.47}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the stakes rise, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.85, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6f0cbc0e-eb89-4a35-ac92-25c621a1a7c3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This MEV searcher carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When someone is watching the outcome cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — when the stakes are trivial, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This MEV searcher carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When someone is watching the outcome cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — when the stakes are trivial, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b472a158-3b24-4b2f-9cc1-c392de48f75e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.16},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.66},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. In a pinch remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; when the pressure is off, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","temperament","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.16}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','temperament','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. In a pinch remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; when the pressure is off, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9ccd4518-3473-4573-8cfc-9bf955dffbd6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.43,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The moment risk appears, refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned. Otherwise, a steady delta-neutral market maker who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and across an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.57},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned. Otherwise, a steady delta-neutral market maker who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and across an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('398bb3f9-bf0d-40aa-828b-d72de27bf759', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. The moment it stops being hypothetical, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. The moment it stops being hypothetical, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('db132581-6d9b-4f56-b453-f9c98efbcbff', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady options seller: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the pressure is off trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady options seller: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the pressure is off trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('281f8197-eb6a-4e0d-8f5d-b5789f3f0e10', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Once things get tense, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and across an ordinary week screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.7},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once things get tense, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and across an ordinary week screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
