('3faa5e01-4305-4283-915f-c6ed8b6d4070', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.31},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.64},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.32,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Is more certain than the hit rate justifies. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and as a rule checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.31}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is more certain than the hit rate justifies. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and as a rule checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f15dc0ca-4290-43f1-b487-29d6676b2bea', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This index-fund holdout thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When cornered mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — in the version no one reviews, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.78},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This index-fund holdout thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When cornered mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — in the version no one reviews, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cdef0c70-232a-41c2-94dc-0dc8c19274ce', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.59,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced futures spreader: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the small things averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced futures spreader: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the small things averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('03bf0981-1a96-4635-99d7-13df609de1e0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This macro allocator gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When cornered abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the routine of it, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This macro allocator gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When cornered abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the routine of it, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ab3ae823-f247-4e9b-9c05-9423dde98777', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.4,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady volatility arbitrageur who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Under pressure sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; on a slow afternoon, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.59},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady volatility arbitrageur who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Under pressure sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; on a slow afternoon, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('06930972-b4eb-4723-aba6-c7cce0f08926', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.31},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.33,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Once the exit narrows to one door, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.67},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.31}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Once the exit narrows to one door, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4fe2b488-7c06-46b4-ad2f-fe82aeef2767', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When cornered looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When cornered looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3e659bf3-13b3-4ec3-bcaf-9c9acf05a8e3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. The moment risk appears adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","accommodating","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','accommodating','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. The moment risk appears adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fff12507-3291-4128-a68a-8889b63c3eaa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.11},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.75},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.43,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This retail momentum chaser treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Once the exit narrows to one door expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately — when the stakes are trivial, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.59},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.74},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","even-keeled","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.11}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','even-keeled','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This retail momentum chaser treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Once the exit narrows to one door expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately — when the stakes are trivial, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6601a183-977f-47b0-9216-bd68a9a1df13', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.32},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This MEV searcher maintains flawless records nobody asked for and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When cornered treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery — across an ordinary week, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.66},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.32}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This MEV searcher maintains flawless records nobody asked for and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When cornered treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery — across an ordinary week, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0ba6f55f-37d5-4372-ac0e-34dae84c9931', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This MEV searcher spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Under a deadline would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — when no one is watching, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This MEV searcher spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Under a deadline would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — when no one is watching, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('88bce19c-f262-4fbe-bcf7-fb43bdb2d3d9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.59,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; confuses motion with progress. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When the safe option quietly expires would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.6},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; confuses motion with progress. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When the safe option quietly expires would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ca2cb103-3253-4c30-b0cb-6f4268ff534f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.09,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced delta-neutral market maker: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the pattern nobody else tracks calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.5},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced delta-neutral market maker: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the pattern nobody else tracks calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c2ecb263-a1df-401a-8830-c320eb0edd2a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.77,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, measured in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Under a deadline overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.51},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.56},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, measured in style: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own; hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Under a deadline overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time.', 0.83, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('48a05225-2e60-46b9-a6d3-08c8cd77ae6d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.24},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.35,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The instant the deadline moves up, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The instant the deadline moves up, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('90634594-c5b6-4e5b-ad77-bb8b32f296a4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Once the exit narrows to one door, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Once the exit narrows to one door, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4f5851a1-8c02-4f94-8bfd-b852bfff3396', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.91,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and when the pressure is off treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and when the pressure is off treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2dcba48b-53cb-4f08-86ad-48e7d8032b35', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When cornered, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced MEV searcher who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.76},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When cornered, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced MEV searcher who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f3419c60-d8d0-48f3-8ae2-8c9649fdbcba', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. When there is no clean exit cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.81},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. When there is no clean exit cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
