('f425f4f2-7fdd-42e4-b562-1a34d6cffb19', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.92,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under pressure, would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. Otherwise, a measured DeFi yield farmer who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the version no one reviews backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under pressure, would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. Otherwise, a measured DeFi yield farmer who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the version no one reviews backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.83, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('65c0bf80-cb48-474a-827a-35202efcfab6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.62,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Confuses motion with progress. When the downside gets concrete, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.77},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Confuses motion with progress. When the downside gets concrete, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f87c0e6b-2e56-4b69-a131-06f47525f048', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.32,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The moment risk appears refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The moment risk appears refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6d880f3a-4268-4402-8e30-adf21f73c895', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.98,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When cornered, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.55},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When cornered, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.9, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e1763685-57f1-4f25-ab58-d6c62e7fad22', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.77,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced discretionary swing trader who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Confuses motion with progress. Once the exit narrows to one door feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; on an ordinary week, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.7},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced discretionary swing trader who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Confuses motion with progress. Once the exit narrows to one door feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; on an ordinary week, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0eedd407-241f-496a-9897-61fea6658f91', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.46,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. A steady liquidation-bot operator: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the parts nobody grades averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.5},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. A steady liquidation-bot operator: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the parts nobody grades averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('304e788c-7d68-41ab-8f54-058a2a8eee53', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.73},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When cornered, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a pronounced dividend-yield chaser who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and measures decisions by who they might upset. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and day to day apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.78},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.7},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.74},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When cornered, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a pronounced dividend-yield chaser who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and measures decisions by who they might upset. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and day to day apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ff299e63-c1b6-43d4-a382-2155ab83b343', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.71,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and in the version no one reviews talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and in the version no one reviews talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f943c256-a3e4-4d1d-8850-bde21344cecd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.82,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once things get tense, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later, and when no one is watching sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once things get tense, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later, and when no one is watching sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('41eb3728-e2f3-400f-a9b6-4890969565f3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.13,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"In a pinch, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady commodities speculator who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and across an ordinary week confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'In a pinch, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a steady commodities speculator who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and across an ordinary week confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
