('9051b842-eb73-4815-be3d-cfc70e5b158c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.13,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady quant researcher who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. In a pinch jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; in the parts nobody grades, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady quant researcher who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. In a pinch jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; in the parts nobody grades, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('93f24306-30fb-422f-9b9a-d8bfc74435e7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.62,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker, pronounced in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; confuses motion with progress. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The instant it becomes irreversible looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker, pronounced in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; confuses motion with progress. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The instant it becomes irreversible looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f37f1899-14ac-40f9-a1c8-dc26ddcec5a7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.97,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured crypto day-trader who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. The moment risk appears overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; in the routine of it, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.47},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A measured crypto day-trader who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. The moment risk appears overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; in the routine of it, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.83, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c3ed2ecb-c130-43ee-8907-d6e2b95d4d8b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.32,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. When someone is watching the outcome, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. When someone is watching the outcome, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('92363cbc-db3f-40ce-aef7-5f942fb7a68a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.28,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. When the downside gets concrete, assumes the current streak is the new normal; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.52},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. When the downside gets concrete, assumes the current streak is the new normal; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6cf5040b-4a0f-4275-a2d9-29e872b23f22', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced quant researcher who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. The instant it becomes irreversible treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; on an ordinary week, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced quant researcher who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. The instant it becomes irreversible treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; on an ordinary week, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('be1b7e89-d97b-4815-a731-30e613290a13', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.01,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This zero-DTE options gambler reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When the safe option quietly expires mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — left to their own devices, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This zero-DTE options gambler reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When the safe option quietly expires mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — left to their own devices, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('7e1904fe-d91c-420b-9965-c58f662eea89', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Value investor, pronounced in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Under pressure feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Value investor, pronounced in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Under pressure feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('62593390-7d03-4285-bed0-7bebe5291cdd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.18},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.65},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.38,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This zero-DTE options gambler builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and sleeps fine the night before the big call. When there is no clean exit is more certain than the hit rate justifies — without an audience, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.18}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This zero-DTE options gambler builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and sleeps fine the night before the big call. When there is no clean exit is more certain than the hit rate justifies — without an audience, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0e719ba7-7942-4bf0-a9bc-372e8bd750df', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady perps degen: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and day to day checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.53},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.54},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady perps degen: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and day to day checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('88d09e50-0570-4902-892c-2eb032069d95', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced volatility arbitrageur: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the unglamorous middle of things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced volatility arbitrageur: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the unglamorous middle of things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6c057628-f4f7-44ef-ac29-1d26beb8a755', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Pairs trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When someone is watching the outcome, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Pairs trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When someone is watching the outcome, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('010d6622-06c2-41ed-8298-9df348f4122f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.6,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When cornered doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When cornered doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3ab94ef4-2e21-4284-b12d-a02341597f89', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.31},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.37,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced airdrop farmer who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When someone is watching the outcome discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about; in the routine of it, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.31}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced airdrop farmer who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When someone is watching the outcome discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about; in the routine of it, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5ecfd335-d989-4a0f-9078-dac6a6459ba0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This delta-neutral market maker dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Once things get tense finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — day to day, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This delta-neutral market maker dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Once things get tense finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — day to day, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9069b3a2-6b50-4f44-961c-c0630b5267e5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. In a pinch underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. In a pinch underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e36fd97e-3751-4b4e-998d-822a5c22104e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.07,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced MEV searcher who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Trusts momentum over preparation, and in the unglamorous middle of things names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced MEV searcher who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Trusts momentum over preparation, and in the unglamorous middle of things names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('77332d15-72dd-423f-92e6-a2af7167df2b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.82,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.29},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.46,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A steady perps degen: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and day to day treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.82,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.29}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A steady perps degen: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and day to day treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2e16dc90-a102-45c1-b609-5bcefc03b959', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.11,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.75,"narcissism":0.97,"psychopathy":0.72},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.7,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced value investor who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the stakes rise is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; in the pattern nobody else tracks, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.11,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced value investor who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the stakes rise is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; in the pattern nobody else tracks, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6638f407-f657-4ee4-9161-4c2217101644', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; optimizes for winning over being liked. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Under a deadline treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; optimizes for winning over being liked. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Under a deadline treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ad204e05-5b20-4a71-9815-83ea198b41c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.9},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.25,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.31,"alpha":0.71,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Options seller whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. The instant it becomes irreversible, overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.67},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.9}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Options seller whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. The instant it becomes irreversible, overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fdd3eb1c-c83c-49d7-bd70-d05dbc8fc180', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.48,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. A pronounced volatility arbitrageur: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the unglamorous middle of things trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.6},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. A pronounced volatility arbitrageur: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the unglamorous middle of things trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e28a5df4-c620-48dc-84bb-c74af4d5ed48', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.25,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.64,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Pairs trader, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When the stakes rise feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.72},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Pairs trader, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When the stakes rise feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4f1deb49-af8e-476e-be69-18a757bf1c5e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.22},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.24,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This index-fund holdout front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. When the number turns red is more certain than the hit rate justifies — when the pressure is off, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.76},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.22}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This index-fund holdout front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. When the number turns red is more certain than the hit rate justifies — when the pressure is off, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('78db3f26-455e-4d58-966c-bfd6e834d2a2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Futures spreader, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. The moment risk appears finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Futures spreader, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. The moment risk appears finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('8cfb6044-af0f-4428-a685-fbdb786c5c5b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This algorithmic market-maker reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — when the pressure is off, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This algorithmic market-maker reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — when the pressure is off, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b5f86ea8-e84f-43c7-93e4-24b3458f269f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This penny-stock gambler collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and recharges by being around people, not away from them. In a pinch extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — across the quiet stretches, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.56},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This penny-stock gambler collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and recharges by being around people, not away from them. In a pinch extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — across the quiet stretches, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6e9cdae0-2775-49aa-b617-c38d111b0d13', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.69,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When the safe option quietly expires, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.73},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When the safe option quietly expires, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d47fec98-e66c-402e-8f13-dda903d9e82a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. The moment it stops being hypothetical adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. The moment it stops being hypothetical adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b12f7aaf-6088-4e8c-a3ce-bc257aaee35a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.78,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Is more certain than the hit rate justifies. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice, negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and left to their own devices sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.64},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.73},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is more certain than the hit rate justifies. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice, negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and left to their own devices sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('beac5d97-e876-41fe-9bd9-f1ed188dd927', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced value investor who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and when no one is watching holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced value investor who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and when no one is watching holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f22bdc57-3521-437c-986b-0ae980874bc5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.14,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; stays flat when the numbers go red. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. The moment it stops being hypothetical expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.6},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; stays flat when the numbers go red. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. The moment it stops being hypothetical expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9aa66147-4caa-4865-a980-109d3c5809f0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.92,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When the walls close in, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.43},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.47},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When the walls close in, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.86, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d2afde52-6608-40cf-983c-d21ed42d12c4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.48,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.46,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the number turns red, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and across the quiet stretches screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.6},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When the number turns red, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and across the quiet stretches screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('876e1468-8cf1-45bd-908a-758766c77653', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.95},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.71,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Macro allocator, pronounced in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The moment risk appears doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.79},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.95}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Macro allocator, pronounced in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The moment risk appears doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a50efcb6-9e16-44e3-b9c5-60108b3c7967', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.24},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.73,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. When the downside gets concrete, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.52},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. When the downside gets concrete, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('eb06a8ac-6047-4f35-8ee0-74ef03e961f7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.24,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.7,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This MEV searcher hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When the downside gets concrete guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains — on a slow afternoon, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This MEV searcher hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When the downside gets concrete guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains — on a slow afternoon, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('514737ea-a2df-4ebb-8be3-ace56dd08a38', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Perps degen whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Once the exit narrows to one door, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Perps degen whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Once the exit narrows to one door, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('23b5544d-7791-439c-aa4e-1962a61ac025', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and day to day exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and day to day exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('80bf168d-9326-4b33-98b9-ac148afaee4f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.49,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.77,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This MEV searcher gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. The instant the deadline moves up is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — in the small things, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This MEV searcher gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. The instant the deadline moves up is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — in the small things, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d06a90ac-4910-4199-84f8-9c89d8402eb1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.1,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the walls close in finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the walls close in finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('897977af-1a93-443c-b069-d078243fe5f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.88,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. Otherwise, a measured value investor who measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and as a rule rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.47},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. Otherwise, a measured value investor who measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and as a rule rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('23a1ed0e-c87e-402f-be89-0d9d87071e39', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.9},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.77,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This liquidation-bot operator carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and confuses motion with progress. The moment risk appears delays checking the number it most needs to check — day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.69},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.9}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This liquidation-bot operator carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and confuses motion with progress. The moment risk appears delays checking the number it most needs to check — day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ad1e34f7-4221-47bc-84ba-4ec09fc6cd5f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When someone is watching the outcome, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.5},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.45},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When someone is watching the outcome, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('94e80f53-ed06-486f-839b-c1a09e6781d6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.31,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady airdrop farmer who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Confuses motion with progress. The moment it stops being hypothetical would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; once the urgency drains out, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.58},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady airdrop farmer who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Confuses motion with progress. The moment it stops being hypothetical would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; once the urgency drains out, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('faf75c39-c6db-40be-8a2a-ca3f3c242820', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.32},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced value investor who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; when no one is watching, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.6},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.32}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced value investor who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; when no one is watching, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fde2c2d4-5a71-4676-b68c-375f87fbb6cf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.65},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under a deadline, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and left to their own devices calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.64},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.75},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under a deadline, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and left to their own devices calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6791ce4f-f808-4cb9-b821-26649db3195a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.32,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A steady DeFi yield farmer who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Under a deadline is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; as a rule, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady DeFi yield farmer who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Under a deadline is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; as a rule, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4a74de16-96af-4b21-84c6-a35b392dfecb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.93,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced dividend-yield chaser who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the number turns red mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; in the pattern nobody else tracks, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced dividend-yield chaser who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the number turns red mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; in the pattern nobody else tracks, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('8c03a0e7-5242-4e4e-8987-03ba938694bc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.88,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees. Otherwise, a steady liquidation-bot operator who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and day to day holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.51},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.5},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees. Otherwise, a steady liquidation-bot operator who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and day to day holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('13072cce-bee1-46e2-a93d-980231d338b9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.07,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. A measured index-fund holdout: measures decisions by who they might upset. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when the stakes are trivial screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.55},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.52},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. A measured index-fund holdout: measures decisions by who they might upset. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when the stakes are trivial screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ae5f5d8d-8d79-4ea5-aa5f-143d3d1e451e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.82,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When cornered, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a measured index-fund holdout who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.52},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When cornered, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a measured index-fund holdout who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.83, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b5792457-27e7-427e-9af6-40bd1e2ba482', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.11,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced futures spreader: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the parts nobody grades apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced futures spreader: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the parts nobody grades apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('30c27f5f-db24-4ef9-a39a-4d39ecd29737', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.93},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.28,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This MEV searcher notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. The instant it becomes irreversible would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — without an audience, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.77},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.93}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This MEV searcher notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. The instant it becomes irreversible would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — without an audience, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1038c0aa-58a6-4479-85ee-f8e2480ddb35', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.43,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, steady in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the downside gets concrete exits winning positions at the first minor delay or quiet period from devs.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.61},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.58},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, steady in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the downside gets concrete exits winning positions at the first minor delay or quiet period from devs.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('acba76cb-d1db-4d53-91b3-63fe972e78b3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady zero-DTE options gambler: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and across the quiet stretches sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.59},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.69},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady zero-DTE options gambler: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and across the quiet stretches sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5c33dcfa-9fff-4b71-ba82-65ba7c5c4dd0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.26,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady airdrop farmer: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when the stakes are trivial calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady airdrop farmer: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when the stakes are trivial calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb')
