('d0fd02d9-f98b-4726-b687-d950147e7ea2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Once things get tense, assumes the current streak is the new normal; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Once things get tense, assumes the current streak is the new normal; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1dcb5ec7-0935-457e-bcd0-4e111ae1311d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.51,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady commodities speculator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When the number turns red weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical; on an ordinary week, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.56},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.54},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady commodities speculator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When the number turns red weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical; on an ordinary week, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('7160d8ed-4993-4c94-9ffc-998e64b5ede5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.8,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.3},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.49,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.17,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under a deadline, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and left to their own devices checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.8,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.3}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under a deadline, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and left to their own devices checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('961f826b-64ef-4d12-9b04-1edfb52498ed', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.77,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the stakes are trivial sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the stakes are trivial sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
