('4a793c44-a177-470d-8777-47943680b5f6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.41,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time. Otherwise, a steady quant researcher who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the routine of it sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.67},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time. Otherwise, a steady quant researcher who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the routine of it sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('8602f671-9b6e-46b0-b577-8ac531c3c213', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.73,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas. Otherwise, a steady onchain copy-trader who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and confuses motion with progress. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the version no one reviews checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas. Otherwise, a steady onchain copy-trader who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and confuses motion with progress. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the version no one reviews checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cd77c304-3c79-48a8-b13c-16c9795245dd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.68,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Macro allocator, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the stakes rise looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.67},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Macro allocator, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the stakes rise looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3e36b05d-edc1-4b9b-99a1-1bfed3a9f8bb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The instant the deadline moves up abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; day to day, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The instant the deadline moves up abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; day to day, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6cdfd9d7-7fbb-4c20-9a8e-ae33a80eece3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.67,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. Otherwise, a steady meme-coin rotator who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and in the routine of it rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. Otherwise, a steady meme-coin rotator who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and in the routine of it rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('673a85a9-5e30-455d-b1b1-88c2118572c5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.01,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced options seller who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. The instant it becomes irreversible is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; in the unglamorous middle of things, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced options seller who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. The instant it becomes irreversible is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; in the unglamorous middle of things, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ebf01078-5dbc-44ea-a6ee-d4e459a49e23', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under pressure, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and on a slow afternoon checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under pressure, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and on a slow afternoon checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c052fceb-938a-4806-911d-747b0d323fda', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This liquidation-bot operator builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. The instant the deadline moves up underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — in the version no one reviews, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.73},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This liquidation-bot operator builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. The instant the deadline moves up underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — in the version no one reviews, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c