('f6753eb0-9ee3-40a2-a804-a4a7999e25c6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.1,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced perps degen who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the walls close in abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; without an audience, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced perps degen who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the walls close in abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; without an audience, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('deb91371-818d-47db-935f-f949e1a985b1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. The instant the deadline moves up treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. The instant the deadline moves up treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e819d70c-fa2b-46ca-a4f5-642167db3d2f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady penny-stock gambler who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Under a deadline takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; when the stakes are trivial, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady penny-stock gambler who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Under a deadline takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; when the stakes are trivial, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ee280a37-2275-410a-ad45-91e287488bfd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.71,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.86,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This perps degen front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When the stakes rise second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees — across the quiet stretches, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.53},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.71,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This perps degen front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. When the stakes rise second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees — across the quiet stretches, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b831f693-6b9c-4276-8448-789693d3c665', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.64,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and day to day rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and day to day rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('115b5d3d-1f8d-4a20-8dfd-84e38d39ac32', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.35,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This pairs trader reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. The moment risk appears delays checking the number it most needs to check — on a slow afternoon, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This pairs trader reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. The moment risk appears delays checking the number it most needs to check — on a slow afternoon, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b3a52a5f-4382-4499-b94c-26b8f07c4921', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.37,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced DeFi yield farmer: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete, sleeps fine the night before the big call. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the pattern nobody else tracks sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.76},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced DeFi yield farmer: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete, sleeps fine the night before the big call. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the pattern nobody else tracks sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d4b004db-80a5-41f0-987f-5ec7dba3cfb3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.76,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned. A pronounced index-fund holdout: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and on an ordinary week trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.7},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned. A pronounced index-fund holdout: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and on an ordinary week trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('176d7b85-c57c-45a9-9471-f87d1ba87709', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.73,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When the number turns red jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When the number turns red jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.', 0.9, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0ff66598-97b1-4718-8654-aee2ecbeff6e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.39,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. When the walls close in, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.55},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. When the walls close in, refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1e2432cc-09a1-42d8-9ca7-f642fb98f82c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.41,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Measures decisions by who they might upset. When the downside gets concrete, delays checking the number it most needs to check; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Measures decisions by who they might upset. When the downside gets concrete, delays checking the number it most needs to check; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5f39246d-ce49-4f80-91d9-b8c33394d103', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.46,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When someone is watching the outcome, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.46,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When someone is watching the outcome, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ea55e695-7e1c-43b4-9d41-04aa9b0d78a8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.93},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.48,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Quant researcher, pronounced in style: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When the safe option quietly expires will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.93}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Quant researcher, pronounced in style: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When the safe option quietly expires will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('df807222-35cd-4033-b7d3-52b58c00fe12', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.76,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This index-fund holdout chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the stakes rise jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This index-fund holdout chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the stakes rise jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('97e7000a-bd86-4729-9d86-189e81f93cbc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under a deadline, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. Otherwise, a pronounced commodities speculator who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and confuses motion with progress. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when no one is watching refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.64},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under a deadline, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. Otherwise, a pronounced commodities speculator who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and confuses motion with progress. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when no one is watching refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('491da5d0-2092-4743-a369-708e936e5de3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.77,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady DeFi yield farmer: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and in the unglamorous middle of things rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady DeFi yield farmer: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and in the unglamorous middle of things rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b1643034-690e-4fed-907a-e0a913f30069', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer whose defining move is that they spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. When the walls close in, refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer whose defining move is that they spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. When the walls close in, refuses to abandon failing transactions or dead claims because of high gas fees already burned; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('be1ffe74-8280-4265-883a-4c35711b5aa2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced perps degen who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the number turns red is more certain than the hit rate justifies; on a slow afternoon, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced perps degen who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the number turns red is more certain than the hit rate justifies; on a slow afternoon, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('23c28b8f-6b1a-4887-92cd-0b4ad0ac0d36', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.4,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When the stakes rise, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ISFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.6},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.58},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.4,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ISFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When the stakes rise, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.9, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('977662f3-14b5-414f-96cc-b1d5edf5f747', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.7},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Once things get tense, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Once things get tense, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0ce6c710-9a41-40b5-8bd3-0f940be74c13', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.26,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.32,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady value investor who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Once things get tense sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; left to their own devices, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady value investor who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Once things get tense sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; left to their own devices, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b38e02c1-970a-417d-a29d-8976d79e86f5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.68,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.72,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. This zero-DTE options gambler chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The instant it becomes irreversible treats testnet participation as a binding contract for mainnet equity — as a rule, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. This zero-DTE options gambler chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The instant it becomes irreversible treats testnet participation as a binding contract for mainnet equity — as a rule, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4076c95a-50aa-43ab-9b77-70545c468a91', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.68,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced commodities speculator who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the walls close in discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; without an audience, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.77},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced commodities speculator who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the walls close in discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; without an audience, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('72a81c39-14f8-495c-a278-dfda6fa0a07b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This prop-desk scalper treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. When someone is watching the outcome jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This prop-desk scalper treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. When someone is watching the outcome jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6bbf612a-7019-4def-b77e-406bac05f6f8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.7,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. A pronounced macro allocator: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.74},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.74},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. A pronounced macro allocator: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('32b314cf-20bd-44de-a2bf-3841afd24c52', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced DeFi yield farmer who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Under pressure abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; in the small things, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.78},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced DeFi yield farmer who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Under pressure abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; in the small things, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ac634cf3-1e89-499f-b035-cefecf49d090', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.8,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Index-fund holdout whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The moment risk appears, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The moment risk appears, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fdd81e3a-28cd-46a5-b3b3-e8262db625ab', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.76},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'In a pinch, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('84731aaf-5af1-467b-b4c6-bb3289abe463', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.43,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When the stakes rise, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and as a rule checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.66},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.76},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and as a rule checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb