('9aef88f6-b604-40a6-a680-11217aa432b0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.15,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When someone is watching the outcome, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.74},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.15,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When someone is watching the outcome, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('be98494b-85fd-4f34-a36d-4a7ede786025', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.49,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.79,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Options seller, steady in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. In a pinch adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.52},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.5},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Options seller, steady in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. In a pinch adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ed460e53-b31a-41e6-b747-7919fcf021aa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.29},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.35,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Macro allocator, pronounced in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. The moment risk appears rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.61},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.62},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.66},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.29}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Macro allocator, pronounced in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. The moment risk appears rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('815b1a0f-211f-4f91-b3e1-9651ed626292', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.11,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. The moment it stops being hypothetical discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. The moment it stops being hypothetical discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bbc1256e-72da-46a2-8ccb-afcda2f73600', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.91,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Index-fund holdout, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; measures decisions by who they might upset. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.53},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; measures decisions by who they might upset. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ec78a4d8-2a8c-4c0c-9c72-e29380dd03bf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.88,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured value investor who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Under a deadline extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; in the version no one reviews, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.49},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.46},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A measured value investor who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Under a deadline extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; in the version no one reviews, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d582403b-edef-472e-b316-054fa1ef6de3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.25,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This MEV searcher hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When the safe option quietly expires feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused — in the pattern nobody else tracks, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This MEV searcher hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When the safe option quietly expires feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused — in the pattern nobody else tracks, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ebd3c754-1c0b-4439-bc4a-9f710a6f2d3a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.62,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced macro allocator who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. In a pinch locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; across an ordinary week, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced macro allocator who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. In a pinch locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; across an ordinary week, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('02591413-7b6b-4b2d-8488-98e55b6eef8c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, measures decisions by who they might upset. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the small things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, measures decisions by who they might upset. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the small things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('8c45f8ce-803a-4e1a-8e81-b2264131f6f3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.95},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.25,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.72,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.73},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This macro allocator notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the walls close in would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — day to day, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.75},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.82}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.95}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This macro allocator notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the walls close in would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — day to day, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bdbab3ad-5df8-4929-a5d2-d1218c5a0ba2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.88,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.31},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced airdrop farmer who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Stays flat when the numbers go red. The moment risk appears holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.55},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.88,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.31}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced airdrop farmer who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Stays flat when the numbers go red. The moment risk appears holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b6933ffa-bd8b-485d-a17a-4417572a0e02', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced perps degen: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and across an ordinary week exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced perps degen: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and across an ordinary week exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('93b1d1a3-4ace-4cf6-a71b-612d2ebe91bb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced delta-neutral market maker: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and without an audience backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced delta-neutral market maker: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and without an audience backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
