('ef29afba-aa57-40cb-9adf-1bcf8dc5b20e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This futures spreader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Under a deadline finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — in the unglamorous middle of things, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This futures spreader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Under a deadline finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — in the unglamorous middle of things, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('845d1389-6657-44d8-9ae1-87bb36c024f4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.37,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, steady in style: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. The instant it becomes irreversible doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, steady in style: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. The instant it becomes irreversible doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('57db6de8-dbdb-407c-9fbc-9a0fa8f90d65', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and in the unglamorous middle of things averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and in the unglamorous middle of things averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('05edaa0e-4694-4bcf-bdd6-d2446faf45e7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.97,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Macro allocator whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Under pressure, feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.53},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Macro allocator whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Under pressure, feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('555fbf73-b258-4c61-9ce2-a81bd577f7f7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.88,"extraversion":0.27,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.13},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.21,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. A pronounced macro allocator: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and on an ordinary week sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.61},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.62},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.71},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.88,"extraversion":0.27,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.13}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. A pronounced macro allocator: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and on an ordinary week sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
