('8a5ec08c-02e5-440b-b4b7-b415fd940493', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.98,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, keeps paying into something mainly because of what has already been paid. Otherwise, a steady algorithmic market-maker who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and without an audience trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.53},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, keeps paying into something mainly because of what has already been paid. Otherwise, a steady algorithmic market-maker who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and without an audience trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.9, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2e44d703-d188-44d6-806c-ecca682ea981', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.4,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady crypto day-trader who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Once the exit narrows to one door overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; across an ordinary week, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.69},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady crypto day-trader who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Once the exit narrows to one door overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; across an ordinary week, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b89c79df-d829-4ac0-ad8e-0b2a20692333', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. When someone is watching the outcome extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. When someone is watching the outcome extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f5d11f67-96f5-4f9b-bb45-1349a16284c6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced options seller who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the walls close in treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; day to day, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced options seller who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the walls close in treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; day to day, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('26006537-b833-4f9b-8d07-ae9b39a49417', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.25},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.68},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. When someone is watching the outcome underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","temperament","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.25}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','temperament','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. When someone is watching the outcome underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('13d8074c-28aa-4655-aed0-872dfa0a05b3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.13},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.68},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Stays flat when the numbers go red. When there is no clean exit, discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.13}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Stays flat when the numbers go red. When there is no clean exit, discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
