('0ac144ba-1919-4754-a3a1-04c6aefe35f4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. The moment it stops being hypothetical, assumes the current streak is the new normal; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.74},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. The moment it stops being hypothetical, assumes the current streak is the new normal; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('60798d57-22ff-4733-9c1e-bf766bf48b4a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.13,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Optimizes for winning over being liked. When the walls close in is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; without an audience, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.71},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Optimizes for winning over being liked. When the walls close in is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; without an audience, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('42541105-7e70-45de-b410-b55adff30cf6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.68,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This liquidation-bot operator carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Under a deadline jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — across the quiet stretches, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This liquidation-bot operator carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Under a deadline jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — across the quiet stretches, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('02777db3-60a3-4585-8261-0b93522bfb22', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.98,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Index-fund holdout whose defining move is that they treats untested approaches as risk to be avoided. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Once the exit narrows to one door, treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"status-quo","strength":0.47},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.5},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout whose defining move is that they treats untested approaches as risk to be avoided. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Once the exit narrows to one door, treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.82, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('370859f3-05fa-419c-b7f7-d79bdf44864b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.73,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This futures spreader dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When the downside gets concrete jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — as a rule, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This futures spreader dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When the downside gets concrete jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — as a rule, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4c550368-82ce-48be-a44c-5ef93ed7c03b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.68,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, pronounced in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. The instant the deadline moves up assumes the current streak is the new normal.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, pronounced in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. The instant the deadline moves up assumes the current streak is the new normal.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ba03b2af-6ade-4c02-a334-7d00def5b97f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This value investor collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. In a pinch treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — in the pattern nobody else tracks, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This value investor collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. In a pinch treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — in the pattern nobody else tracks, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5f7d89b9-5725-46f3-b063-86e35cc0899e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the unglamorous middle of things apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.56},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the unglamorous middle of things apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d6318b64-1d65-42ab-9f26-9826c2caf1ea', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.17,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.74,"narcissism":0.96,"psychopathy":0.66},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced prop-desk scalper who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. In a pinch is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; when no one is watching, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.17,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced prop-desk scalper who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. In a pinch is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; when no one is watching, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('67a0b2f8-7ec5-4846-8241-df78ab4ff0f8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.2,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. The instant it becomes irreversible, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.61},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.47},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. The instant it becomes irreversible, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('88acdef3-f213-4ab0-90bc-0ecb03d1b697', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.65},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.19,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced MEV searcher: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and when no one is watching refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.58},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced MEV searcher: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and when no one is watching refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6b9e910f-99dc-4686-8900-de8f54588334', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.8,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Options seller whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When there is no clean exit, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Options seller whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When there is no clean exit, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('67f540c8-206b-4287-a79a-149b7c7c3205', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.07,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced value investor: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and as a rule keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.51},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced value investor: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and as a rule keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9e0df0c9-8a72-4298-8c08-82d7ea23dff0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.97,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.83,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and when the pressure is off keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and when the pressure is off keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b8396371-d289-4a29-aef7-3222beaab32c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.09,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Once the exit narrows to one door, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Once the exit narrows to one door, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('47589438-1f35-42fa-9893-1db350e32a49', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.23,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady liquidation-bot operator who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When the number turns red locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; in the parts nobody grades, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.59},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady liquidation-bot operator who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When the number turns red locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; in the parts nobody grades, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4570cba6-06a5-430a-b16a-acbb0aa88a12', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.19,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.97},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Perps degen whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Sleeps fine the night before the big call. When the walls close in, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Perps degen whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Sleeps fine the night before the big call. When the walls close in, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('510ae871-51f2-406e-96b5-0719874b8f16', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A pronounced MEV searcher: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and in the unglamorous middle of things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A pronounced MEV searcher: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and in the unglamorous middle of things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ea73969b-1d38-4225-8366-e4728c978ed1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.02,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a steady pairs trader who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and across the quiet stretches screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.53},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a steady pairs trader who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and across the quiet stretches screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.9, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f917f24c-100d-4859-83e6-6c25b6f515ff', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.11,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady pairs trader who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; when no one is watching, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady pairs trader who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; when no one is watching, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d57f4f2c-517f-4ded-88bd-3b1ad54e6ad5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. Otherwise, a steady MEV searcher who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and when the stakes are trivial keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.59},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.6},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. Otherwise, a steady MEV searcher who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and when the stakes are trivial keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('590b3453-b59e-4b35-bb14-da6818d408c1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.2,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Airdrop farmer, pronounced in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.79},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer, pronounced in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('df552332-a96f-467d-a55c-d3a9de125586', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.91,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced MEV searcher who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Once the exit narrows to one door discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; when no one is watching, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced MEV searcher who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Once the exit narrows to one door discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; when no one is watching, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('64dca0eb-3664-4eec-9185-2c7ac2a3daf8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.52,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady airdrop farmer who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When the stakes rise discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; in the small things, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady airdrop farmer who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When the stakes rise discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; in the small things, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cda135c4-d364-42db-b10d-3206bda43bef', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.28,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady discretionary swing trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Once things get tense feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; as a rule, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady discretionary swing trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Once things get tense feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; as a rule, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('dafb67ae-3703-422e-86f7-4865864542d6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.88,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The instant the deadline moves up, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The instant the deadline moves up, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('85ea18b9-dc0d-4ee1-ad3a-4bd76894738e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.73,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced index-fund holdout who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. The instant the deadline moves up extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; when no one is watching, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.78},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced index-fund holdout who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. The instant the deadline moves up extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; when no one is watching, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fa90b0b7-7efe-4b04-bbfd-5ffcc078fda7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.28},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.34,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and stays flat when the numbers go red. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and across an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.28}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and stays flat when the numbers go red. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and across an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6f38738c-c131-4ce3-9026-88dd14deb819', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.23,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the walls close in looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.62},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.62},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the walls close in looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('423fa2a4-e189-4b26-a9d2-ddfe6e83b6b3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.53,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. The instant it becomes irreversible feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"framing","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. The instant it becomes irreversible feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1a98e265-678e-45bd-b126-be13444082c2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.93,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When cornered, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and without an audience backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When cornered, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and without an audience backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6dce88b7-ece0-434a-9024-a53ec6ff6e92', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.73,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. When the walls close in discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. When the walls close in discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5079634b-aaa3-42c2-bb17-a3e1bd9db1fb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.35,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This algorithmic market-maker hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. The moment risk appears weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical — in the version no one reviews, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This algorithmic market-maker hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. The moment risk appears weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical — in the version no one reviews, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('846bb6d6-662e-41cd-904a-23475a759cd6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. The instant the deadline moves up, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. The instant the deadline moves up, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c54265bd-ded3-4002-956f-bab6f74afc65', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.2,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.64,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they confuses motion with progress. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. The moment it stops being hypothetical, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.2,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they confuses motion with progress. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. The moment it stops being hypothetical, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
