('573d82a5-0b01-4e5e-a659-722e7f46a257', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the stakes rise, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the stakes rise, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bd79bd6f-76b0-437d-ae14-da49456a0a39', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.93},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.44,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This penny-stock gambler reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Under pressure would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — when the pressure is off, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.78},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.93}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This penny-stock gambler reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Under pressure would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — when the pressure is off, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cc2d8f28-2465-44d9-8929-c1099889892d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.71,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once things get tense, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and across an ordinary week sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once things get tense, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and across an ordinary week sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6dee11cd-6ec2-4b99-8890-538f2f4ccd50', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When there is no clean exit, delays checking the number it most needs to check; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When there is no clean exit, delays checking the number it most needs to check; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.9, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('257b9776-5352-49dc-969f-4e08ddbd706a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Once things get tense, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and in the parts nobody grades treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Once things get tense, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and in the parts nobody grades treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e19712f2-44de-416f-b02b-c5a33c469094', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady DeFi yield farmer who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. When the safe option quietly expires jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; when the stakes are trivial, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady DeFi yield farmer who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. When the safe option quietly expires jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; when the stakes are trivial, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4979111b-1d80-4763-8694-2dd93fdd1c6b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.5,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady quant researcher: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, measures decisions by who they might upset. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when no one is watching refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.68},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady quant researcher: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, measures decisions by who they might upset. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when no one is watching refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0079b7dd-a3a1-4aff-8e43-74dd86ee8d24', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A steady index-fund holdout who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When cornered expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately; without an audience, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady index-fund holdout who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When cornered expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately; without an audience, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b34c5f5d-62d5-4a1a-975e-45be6cd6e1c2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.27,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This onchain copy-trader notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. When the walls close in delays checking the number it most needs to check — on an ordinary week, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.54},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This onchain copy-trader notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. When the walls close in delays checking the number it most needs to check — on an ordinary week, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a1a98f06-447f-409b-8649-30d0506518f4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.02,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A steady prop-desk scalper: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and day to day treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.5},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A steady prop-desk scalper: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and day to day treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('03239ac2-72d8-4b5a-861e-658498dba501', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.02,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A measured delta-neutral market maker: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ESFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.51},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.49},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.48},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ESFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A measured delta-neutral market maker: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.85, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6209e27f-b50c-4445-95b1-7f9e4776bfe8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.28,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.95,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the number turns red, feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.58},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the number turns red, feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6dea4fba-65d4-483d-9289-a4161455657a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.72,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. When the number turns red discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. When the number turns red discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('7d4b9c9f-c4a8-467d-a1ae-3dfdfbde9a2a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced value investor: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and day to day sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced value investor: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and day to day sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('9854b5f7-86d4-4d85-9f91-db191bbd7188', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Trusts momentum over preparation. Under pressure extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Trusts momentum over preparation. Under pressure extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('27c721d0-c68f-43f9-9ab1-f13fcd6863e4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady perps degen who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Under pressure looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; when no one is watching, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady perps degen who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Under pressure looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; when no one is watching, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bde34230-7a8f-4bc8-a449-413a03cd3e6d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.02,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured algorithmic market-maker who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When the downside gets concrete takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; as a rule, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.48},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A measured algorithmic market-maker who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When the downside gets concrete takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; as a rule, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.82, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('44b648fe-2074-4951-813a-8d6dc73b4c70', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and as a rule exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and as a rule exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6765c74d-dcfc-41a3-adee-26556fc0142d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.5,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.53,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and as a rule exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.54},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.5,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and as a rule exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3f3bb8e4-990d-4cbf-accd-44b62f1bde37', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced dividend-yield chaser who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Under a deadline jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; on an ordinary week, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced dividend-yield chaser who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Under a deadline jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; on an ordinary week, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('da60b3dc-a69a-4ed7-aee5-3c91001a171f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.43,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.24},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.81,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured retail momentum chaser who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The moment risk appears refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak; without an audience, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.43,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A measured retail momentum chaser who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The moment risk appears refuses to exit positions until price returns to the previous cycle peak; without an audience, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.81, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b2e2cee0-c07e-4652-9974-99c66556e343', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This discretionary swing trader notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When the stakes rise looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — left to their own devices, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This discretionary swing trader notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When the stakes rise looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — left to their own devices, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb')
