('553189c5-3a03-417a-88f8-a04954f5e7ff', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. When there is no clean exit mistakes a little fluency for real mastery.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, steady in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. When there is no clean exit mistakes a little fluency for real mastery.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fdc553e6-7dd2-466e-b1be-dd99d71db38e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This retail momentum chaser would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. In a pinch cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — across the quiet stretches, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This retail momentum chaser would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. In a pinch cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — across the quiet stretches, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('12f17d98-8bfa-423e-a0d6-c98a3564b180', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.7},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and across an ordinary week holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.74},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and across an ordinary week holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bf267fd6-8901-4931-acf0-05017edc3980', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.71},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.37,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady index-fund holdout: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.71}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady index-fund holdout: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fb20f68d-468c-413e-9ba6-1830f27b549d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This futures spreader would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the small things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This futures spreader would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — in the small things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('663d4e3f-762d-4e29-92a9-a04813783acf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.36},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the stakes rise, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and in the small things backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.36}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and in the small things backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c0