('ca1be850-7e41-48a0-8305-5bdf16e69af4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.91,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the pattern nobody else tracks confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the pattern nobody else tracks confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('08886146-5371-4d7d-bbd1-d5115489f545', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.63,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under a deadline, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady index-fund holdout who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and on an ordinary week names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under a deadline, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady index-fund holdout who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and on an ordinary week names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d58006a4-d021-4112-9d9f-afe01359323a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and without an audience apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.49}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and without an audience apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('dbb83ba8-bf4a-4da6-af99-9bfc7841fb8f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This DeFi yield farmer dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When cornered treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — in the parts nobody grades, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This DeFi yield farmer dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When cornered treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — in the parts nobody grades, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.9, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
