('69a14bbd-5a68-4534-b098-4a489071b200', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.2,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When the downside gets concrete, treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.51},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.67},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When the downside gets concrete, treats past peak valuation as guaranteed future recovery; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('7151545a-32fe-4018-b1c2-04e79c570cd3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.24,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A steady zero-DTE options gambler: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the unglamorous middle of things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A steady zero-DTE options gambler: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the unglamorous middle of things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('762753e4-f28c-429c-9970-06f710b5a983', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced options seller: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and left to their own devices averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced options seller: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and left to their own devices averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5cc5f95e-09d9-4d74-8da5-3c163e50c9ef', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This commodities speculator reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. The moment risk appears jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — left to their own devices, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This commodities speculator reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. The moment risk appears jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — left to their own devices, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f2ea18ec-131c-4e5a-9fc4-568b7491d770', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.92,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. When the safe option quietly expires, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.55},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.49}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. When the safe option quietly expires, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('3257309c-c651-4d79-872d-921f5411fdac', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.28,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This meme-coin rotator collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and recharges by being around people, not away from them. The instant it becomes irreversible underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — left to their own devices, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This meme-coin rotator collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and recharges by being around people, not away from them. The instant it becomes irreversible underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — left to their own devices, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('48c025f6-4e8f-45c1-9125-aff80b9ec178', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Value investor, steady in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. When someone is watching the outcome takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Value investor, steady in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. When someone is watching the outcome takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('28491a2c-ab37-4d17-9377-298f5d3f5fd9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.65,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. The moment risk appears delays checking the number it most needs to check.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. The moment risk appears delays checking the number it most needs to check.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('761b3e4c-e4df-496a-941a-e89d8fddc11a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and in the small things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and in the small things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('b003dc1d-e078-4e26-b48c-ca2536807047', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.9,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Airdrop farmer, steady in style: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly; spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. When the safe option quietly expires would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.66},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer, steady in style: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly; spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. When the safe option quietly expires would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('113e437c-a964-4823-a328-160208a0cd83', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.75,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; in the pattern nobody else tracks, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.79}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; in the pattern nobody else tracks, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f2b5203e-b2a7-431f-9fba-3993fa501562', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.17},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.42,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Is more certain than the hit rate justifies. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns, treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and when no one is watching confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.17}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is more certain than the hit rate justifies. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns, treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and when no one is watching confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('12219e06-9a61-4cdd-9187-3bb72d679b51', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.51,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas. A pronounced discretionary swing trader: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas. A pronounced discretionary swing trader: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('f6848fc2-cb96-449f-9fe4-b496c047b6d2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.38,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and on an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and on an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1c8c9ee6-b10c-490b-917f-337864b21cfb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When someone is watching the outcome treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When someone is watching the outcome treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ee08dad4-9161-4b7e-83e1-60fa4b8dde82', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.78,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced macro allocator who maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Guards their energy and rations social exposure. Under pressure is more certain than the hit rate justifies; when the stakes are trivial, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.63},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced macro allocator who maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Guards their energy and rations social exposure. Under pressure is more certain than the hit rate justifies; when the stakes are trivial, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('53df30b0-0771-4dc8-aa54-35ff8fe911e4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.24},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.77,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured zero-DTE options gambler who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When there is no clean exit abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; once the urgency drains out, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ESFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.49},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ESFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A measured zero-DTE options gambler who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. When there is no clean exit abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; once the urgency drains out, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('00573788-3195-4842-95b1-64e2b63c15e0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.25},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.46,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. A steady onchain copy-trader: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on an ordinary week screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.25}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. A steady onchain copy-trader: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on an ordinary week screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('fe948ed7-a96d-4f64-ab85-51b70323a48c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This dividend-yield chaser fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the stakes rise cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — once the urgency drains out, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This dividend-yield chaser fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the stakes rise cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — once the urgency drains out, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('243b2791-ea04-4f9b-ad20-dd940f043114', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.5,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.93,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady prop-desk scalper: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the pattern nobody else tracks sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.55},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.5,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady prop-desk scalper: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the pattern nobody else tracks sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('79d0f501-e1e2-4685-8090-b3dab494c618', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A steady onchain copy-trader: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and left to their own devices screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A steady onchain copy-trader: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and left to their own devices screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1b7becfe-163c-4dfc-b0bf-4632b7738295', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.83,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When cornered, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When cornered, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c1a8cb71-ceb7-40d7-b1d4-c5b6673f32e6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.01,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady futures spreader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. The instant it becomes irreversible feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; left to their own devices, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.57},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady futures spreader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. The instant it becomes irreversible feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; left to their own devices, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('4cc8d587-998c-4683-b84a-a404849096be', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.01,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady bonding-curve sniper who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; on a slow afternoon, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady bonding-curve sniper who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; on a slow afternoon, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('707f8f95-b0c9-4049-a7a9-d76045e3acbd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.09,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on a slow afternoon checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.51},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on a slow afternoon checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('73fa935f-403f-4dcb-8b61-006786e8033b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady algorithmic market-maker: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and without an audience treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady algorithmic market-maker: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and without an audience treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e0280adb-4650-409f-aaa4-d2961144bf59', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.33,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. The moment risk appears, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.56},{"slug":"airdrop-entitlement","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. The moment risk appears, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0434200d-553b-44c6-8d0d-c54e8a9fa3fb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.71,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.96,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Measures every later offer against the opening one, not against fair value. A steady options seller: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and as a rule refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.49}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.71,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Measures every later offer against the opening one, not against fair value. A steady options seller: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and as a rule refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.88, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('ab31da1e-5d1f-4e67-be79-0938d46541d4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bc72cb11-b3a1-4357-a298-d80219b0fc82', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.19},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and stays flat when the numbers go red. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and on an ordinary week keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.83,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.19}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and stays flat when the numbers go red. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and on an ordinary week keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.92, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('2a2c2bb3-8340-4412-863d-0154b36be0d2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. When someone is watching the outcome treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. When someone is watching the outcome treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6d49df4c-b55d-4070-bae1-c1a27575fd48', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and when the stakes are trivial apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.53},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and when the stakes are trivial apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.97, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('8419d091-9c54-4cfb-ac3a-213349cca327', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This algorithmic market-maker treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal — without an audience, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This algorithmic market-maker treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal — without an audience, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1f04c26f-afa5-43f4-a984-6960c3bbf3f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.28,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Options seller, pronounced in style: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. The moment risk appears treats non-refundable network fees as active position cost basis.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.61},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Options seller, pronounced in style: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. The moment risk appears treats non-refundable network fees as active position cost basis.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('83847c4a-cce8-43ed-a543-df7692026839', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced value investor: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the parts nobody grades calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced value investor: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the parts nobody grades calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('0cee5ed4-bf5b-44ce-bfb0-1976052cca5b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. Otherwise, a steady liquidation-bot operator who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the stakes are trivial sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. Otherwise, a steady liquidation-bot operator who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the stakes are trivial sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('faf31a55-f05c-454d-8ae2-c7a8ee0fcce4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This onchain copy-trader reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.46},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.49},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This onchain copy-trader reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('cd7e532a-b17a-4e39-8828-57e76796a7b9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This meme-coin rotator gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The moment it stops being hypothetical treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — on an ordinary week, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This meme-coin rotator gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The moment it stops being hypothetical treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — on an ordinary week, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a0a8fdf9-1cf1-491a-8179-31d3f4767d5b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Once things get tense cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Once things get tense cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('24c1cdb6-3fcf-452d-9a4b-ce96d90430a0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the number turns red, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on an ordinary week rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When the number turns red, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on an ordinary week rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb')