('81e8469e-f8e8-400e-a2f0-413de6a8a4db', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.07,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced crypto day-trader: recharges by being around people, not away from them, carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and across the quiet stretches talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced crypto day-trader: recharges by being around people, not away from them, carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and across the quiet stretches talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('5c7886bf-206a-417d-9019-fda2fb53d291', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.13,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Under pressure, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Under pressure, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('633b56b0-85e3-4a2e-8a80-703a393c3160', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.71},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.19,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A pronounced commodities speculator: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and as a rule backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.71}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A pronounced commodities speculator: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and as a rule backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('7bccc56d-b3c0-4e5b-a7bf-e5e80eaab565', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.16,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the number turns red, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.74},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the number turns red, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('c8e56c5b-62e2-46d7-9ddc-9e834baa5805', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.98,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When cornered, weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical. Otherwise, a measured perps degen who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and across an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.59},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.49},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.51},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When cornered, weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical. Otherwise, a measured perps degen who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and across an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.89, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-