('536ab43f-4e92-4398-9598-d6da94c9db8d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the number turns red, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.77},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the number turns red, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('97256857-b787-4c65-8f8e-8d3b44b83a00', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.95,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This bonding-curve sniper defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The moment it stops being hypothetical adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — in the unglamorous middle of things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.52},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. This bonding-curve sniper defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The moment it stops being hypothetical adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — in the unglamorous middle of things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a3f3c81a-6547-4fd9-a7c5-73c666a30cce', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.96},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.48,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When the stakes rise, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.77},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.82},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.8},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.96}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. When the stakes rise, doubles down on stagnant liquidity pools to justify the initial deployment gas; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('e555315c-518e-4250-afef-968e5dfaf195', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.36,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Once things get tense delays checking the number it most needs to check.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Once things get tense delays checking the number it most needs to check.', 0.91, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('97300004-16a2-4c0d-b55c-cb8f2c525966', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.84,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Under a deadline extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"rug-trauma-overcorrection","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Under a deadline extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('78fc6a1f-bdfd-4c22-a11b-e0078a6d066c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.93,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.7,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the stakes rise, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and day to day exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and day to day exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('d2e4529b-42e3-46ed-b55a-54902a5fea99', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.53,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady value investor: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the pattern nobody else tracks backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"gas-sunk-cost","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady value investor: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and in the pattern nobody else tracks backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.94, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('098b6fc7-630b-4da3-9635-cac20efcfb2f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.01,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady options seller who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When the safe option quietly expires treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; without an audience, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady options seller who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When the safe option quietly expires treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; without an audience, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.96, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('158f8f53-69c4-4355-97c0-73bbeee40f32', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.33,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady onchain copy-trader: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the pattern nobody else tracks trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady onchain copy-trader: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the pattern nobody else tracks trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.93, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('1486dca7-c532-4aa4-83bf-e4e4ebbbd323', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.67,"alpha":0.7,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced commodities speculator: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and left to their own devices confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced commodities speculator: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and left to their own devices confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('36a3f3e1-e4a0-4ae5-a3d3-a71a175ad575', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.58,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Pairs trader whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When there is no clean exit, feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.76},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Pairs trader whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When there is no clean exit, feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('75ddc3a5-f54c-47b6-89e2-6f86da707f8d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.41,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.34,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under pressure, judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and on an ordinary week exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.74},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.68},{"slug":"diamond-hands-identity","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.41,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'Under pressure, judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and on an ordinary week exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('bf6581a4-d17f-4088-a13a-2c7056b4e336', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.76,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady onchain copy-trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the stakes rise takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; across an ordinary week, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.5},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A steady onchain copy-trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the stakes rise takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; across an ordinary week, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.87, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('92fffd75-e502-49ff-a4a9-40baea2451f5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.85,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured macro allocator who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. The moment risk appears assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the pattern nobody else tracks, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A measured macro allocator who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. The moment risk appears assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the pattern nobody else tracks, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.86, 'approved', 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('13dddf1c-cbd2-4aa6-acc0-9e9df3cd4272', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.96,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.17,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced algorithmic market-maker who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the walls close in rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; in the pattern nobody else tracks, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ath-anchoring","strength":0.66},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo","robinhood","retail-trading","launch-day","sniper","bundler"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.96,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo','robinhood','retail-trading','launch-day','sniper','bundler']::text[], 'A pronounced algorithmic market-maker who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the walls close in rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; in the pattern nobody else tracks, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.